    "discriminators": [
     "A big lever: heavy metal-on-metal CLANK and CLUNK, with audible travel and a solid end stop. Much lower and heavier than MECHANICAL-CLICK or MECHANICAL-SWITCH - low_band_energy and a long metallic decay are the cue. Frankenstein knife switches, breaker levers, track levers.",
